		"description": "Advanced API collection for Energy Sports Meet Console.\nFeatures:\n- **Automated Auth**: Login once, token applies globally.\n- **Pre-request Scripts**: Auto-injects token.\n- **Environment Variables**: Base URL & Token management.\n- **Role-Based Handlers**: Organized folders for Admin, Sports Head, Committee, Scorer.",
